text: "Wish I Didn't Know Now" is a 1994 song by country singer Toby Keith and is the fourth and final single from his debut studio album Toby Keith. It went to number 2 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart and number 17 on the Canadian RPM Country Tracks chart. ==Notes== Category:1994 songs Category:Country songs Category:Toby Keith songs
title: Wish I Didn't Know Now
